{"tid":1431293,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(文宣入黎) 3毛搞hashtag撐警","createTime":"2019-08-08T03:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T06:08:09.000Z","uid":99395,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5f1ca592f54d30a13013da9e490bed2eac1b8593","tid":1431293,"uid":99395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WLUk4ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWLUk4ba.jpg&h=e8aeeaf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8月10日用以下hashtag洗版<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#全民撐警<br />\n#守護香港</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n等市民分享電視睇唔到嘅畫面"},{"pid":"4a4bcb126d82ea85b5ba5c20ccb89beab157ca66","tid":1431293,"uid":99395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:13:15.000Z","msg":"團體發起8.10「全民撐警日」 支持警員維護法紀 - 大公報"},{"pid":"e9391ffd16ea4f715e59d2a59b11a83b374cf316","tid":1431293,"uid":158889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:13:54.000Z","msg":"唔係唔一齊分享啊?"},{"pid":"13e7f31a9de05e9f475d9fb5a376ac6dc15cf543","tid":1431293,"uid":34020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:17:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cm36bK9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcm36bK9.jpg&h=5ce2c060&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V87yBbR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV87yBbR.jpg&h=cd0a3348&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pQ95six.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpQ95six.jpg&h=297b81e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84f4ee187a8beeb252dd90208f0c32726b338a64","tid":1431293,"uid":99395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:26:37.000Z","msg":"要整多d文宣圖俾大家果日post"},{"pid":"de40e16197bdf2fa4f31240e2464ad0b19bfcd5b","tid":1431293,"uid":99395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:27:57.000Z","msg":"守護香港大聯盟號召：<br />\n<br />\n8月10日「全民撐警日」活動。請  大力支持，踴躍參與:<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n1.     請偕同親朋戚友於8月10日自發前往當區/附近警署，送上心意卡或慰問信、感謝信，向警務人員表達慰問和支持。<br />\n<br />\n2.     請將心意卡、慰問信、感謝信拍攝上傳到社交媒體(如朋友圈、群組、Facebook、Instagram、Twitter等等)分享，並在帖內輸入Hashtags #全民撐警、#守護香港。<br />\n<br />\n3.     當日穿著藍色上衣:「全民穿藍，香港天藍」。<br />\n<br />\n4.     遇到警員時主動問候，如點頭微笑講「早晨!」、「辛苦曬! 多謝你！」，或做「Like」的動作表示讚賞。<br />\n<br />\n5.     到警方網站、Facebook上留言點讚。<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHongKongPoliceForce%2F&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rKnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=9e995916\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce/</a><br />\n<br />\n6.     在網上填寫嘉許表格，對警員進行讚賞。<a href=\"https://www1.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/EGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI/ereport_details?report=CMPLT_TO_POLICE_OFCR&amp;fontSize=100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.erc.police.gov.hk%2Fcmiserc%2FEGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI%2Fereport_details%3Freport%3DCMPLT_TO_POLICE_OFCR%26fontSize%3D100&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rKnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=ebdb187a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/EGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI/ereport_details?report=CMPLT_TO_POLICE_OFCR&amp;fontSize=100</a><br />\n<br />\n7.     屆時請留意當區動態，以令活動順利。<br />\n<br />\n8.     按以下連結查詢附近警署地址，以方便大家前往慰問。<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2GPMs6x\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2GPMs6x&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rKnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=ec713f3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2GPMs6x</a>"},{"pid":"cf477a36d3bff96f95df921711a7ab77c3a12639","tid":1431293,"uid":261332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:29:57.000Z","msg":"維穩費咁快洗哂？<br />\n唔搞集會嗱今次？"},{"pid":"8fdb1c89260b7b8ff0ec926c30d325b8f4b69a40","tid":1431293,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:08:09.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}